was so popular.

487
00:18:48,333 --> 00:18:50,125
How could I not notice that?

488
00:18:50,208 --> 00:18:51,916
Ya get it now, Nagasumi?

489
00:18:52,000 --> 00:18:53,166
[NAGASUMI] Chimp.

490
00:18:53,250 --> 00:18:54,583
Now you're beginning to
see how it actually is.

491
00:18:54,666 --> 00:18:55,958
There are plenty
of guys in this school

492
00:18:56,041 --> 00:18:57,875
who care about
her more than you do.

493
00:18:57,958 --> 00:19:02,375
[SARU] That's right, Nagasumi!
Never forget that love is war!

494
00:19:02,458 --> 00:19:04,500
[NAGASUMI] Please
teach me Chimp Roshi!

495
00:19:04,583 --> 00:19:06,458
[SARU] Huh?
It looks like a storm is

496
00:19:06,541 --> 00:19:08,791
beginning to brew
in the distance.

497
00:19:10,958 --> 00:19:15,041
Uh, you there, Sun Seto,
why don't you try solving it.

498
00:19:15,125 --> 00:19:16,208
Yes sir.

499
00:19:16,291 --> 00:19:18,125
[SUN] Um, uh.

500
00:19:18,208 --> 00:19:19,333
[BOY A] Hang in there Sun!

501
00:19:19,416 --> 00:19:20,916
[BOY B] You can do it.
You're a smart girl!

502
00:19:21,000 --> 00:19:22,500
[BOY C] Sun!

503
00:19:22,583 --> 00:19:23,916
I know Miss Sun
is popular,

504
00:19:24,000 --> 00:19:26,750
but this much enthusiasm
is ridiculous.

505
00:19:26,833 --> 00:19:30,125
[MASA] Okay, Lunar Edomae.
You try the next problem.

506
00:19:30,208 --> 00:19:31,666
[Lunar fake weeps]

507
00:19:31,750 --> 00:19:32,916
Hm?
What's wrong?

508
00:19:33,000 --> 00:19:36,666
I'm sorry, Mister Masa.
I don't know it!

509
00:19:36,750 --> 00:19:38,041
Come on now!

510
00:19:38,125 --> 00:19:40,083
This is a pretty easy problem
to solve, you know.

511
00:19:40,166 --> 00:19:42,125
[BOY A] How could say that
to a brand new student?

512
00:19:42,208 --> 00:19:43,500
[BOY B] Yeah, poor Lunar!

513
00:19:43,583 --> 00:19:45,500
[BOY C] That's mean,
giving her such a hard problem!

514
00:19:45,583 --> 00:19:47,458
[BOY D] Apologize
to Lunar, you scumbag!

515
00:19:47,541 --> 00:19:48,666
Hey now!

516
00:19:48,750 --> 00:19:51,541
You don't have to be
so hard on Mister Masa!

517
00:19:54,291 --> 00:19:56,875
[LUNAR] As if that problem
was actually difficult for us!

518
00:19:57,208 --> 00:19:58,291
[CLASS REP] Stop shouting.

519
00:19:58,375 --> 00:19:59,458
If you boys could
just calm down a little.

520
00:19:59,541 --> 00:20:00,708
[MAWARI] Boys,
if you don't shut up soon,

521
00:20:00,791 --> 00:20:03,291
you're all going to be
rounded up and arrested!

522
00:20:03,708 --> 00:20:05,708
--[LUNA FACTION] Lunar! Lunar!
--[SUN FACTION] Sun! Sun!

523
00:20:05,791 --> 00:20:08,875
[NAGASUMI] Uh oh...
What's going on with everyone?

524
00:20:09,250 --> 00:20:10,500
[NAGASUMI] The class
has split into people

525
00:20:10,583 --> 00:20:13,416
rooting for Lunar and
people rooting for Sun.

526
00:20:13,791 --> 00:20:16,166
[MASA] Hey, these kids
are just ordinary humans.

527
00:20:16,250 --> 00:20:18,416
What have you done
to get them like this?

528
00:20:18,500 --> 00:20:21,500
Don't you think you're taking
your mischief a bit too far?

529
00:20:21,583 --> 00:20:22,791
[LUNAR] Now, now,
we haven't done

530
00:20:22,875 --> 00:20:24,083
anything to the children.

531
00:20:24,166 --> 00:20:26,208
The boys are getting
excited all on their own.

532
00:20:26,291 --> 00:20:27,583
What's a girl to do?

533
00:20:27,666 --> 00:20:29,041
[Lunar laughs]

534
00:20:29,125 --> 00:20:31,500
[LUNA FACTION] Lunar!

535
00:20:31,583 --> 00:20:34,250
[SUN FACTION] Sun!

536
00:20:34,333 --> 00:20:37,166
Has this been bottled
up inside everybody all along?

537
00:20:37,250 --> 00:20:40,708
[SARU] Young Nagasumi,
you still don't understand.

538
00:20:40,791 --> 00:20:41,958
[NAGASUMI] Chimp Roshi!

539
00:20:42,041 --> 00:20:43,708
Lunar's transfer to
this school activated

540
00:20:43,791 --> 00:20:46,208
the fans she's had
here the whole time.

541
00:20:46,291 --> 00:20:47,625
[SARU] That triggered
the sentiments festering

542
00:20:47,708 --> 00:20:49,625
inside Sun's own
fan base to leave

543
00:20:49,708 --> 00:20:52,083
dormancy and
rise to the surface.

544
00:20:52,166 --> 00:20:53,916
These two surges
have had the effect

545
00:20:54,000 --> 00:20:56,208
of polarizing the class,
and the two groups

546
00:20:56,291 --> 00:20:58,250
are now going to collide.

547
00:20:58,916 --> 00:21:00,458
[NAGASUMI] What?

548
00:21:00,541 --> 00:21:02,916
[BOY A] Are the two of you
siding with Lunar or Sun?

549
00:21:03,000 --> 00:21:04,375
[SARU] This violent
maelstrom will

550
00:21:04,458 --> 00:21:06,500
spread ever wider
as time passes.

551
00:21:06,583 --> 00:21:08,458
Now that the great
tide of conflict

552
00:21:08,541 --> 00:21:10,333
has begun, no one can stop it.

553
00:21:10,416 --> 00:21:14,791
Isono Eighth Junior High School
will inevitably be rent in two.

554
00:21:14,875 --> 00:21:17,416
[SARU] A new era
has begun now, Nagasumi!

555
00:21:17,500 --> 00:21:19,125
What the hell
is going on here?

556
00:21:19,208 --> 00:21:20,458
And what about
our classes?

557
00:21:20,541 --> 00:21:22,166
[CLASS REP]
Boys are so volatile.

558
00:21:22,250 --> 00:21:25,958
Are all you boys morons?
Stop now! Come on!

559
00:21:27,333 --> 00:21:28,750
[Maki groans]

560
00:21:28,833 --> 00:21:34,416
[MAKI] I'm coming, Miss Sun.
Maki's here. I'll help you.

561
00:21:39,666 --> 00:21:41,541
Damn you Lunar!

562
00:21:47,458 --> 00:21:50,625
[Lunar laughs wickedly]

563
00:21:50,708 --> 00:21:54,166
[LUNAR] Yes, everything
is going according to plan.

564
00:21:54,500 --> 00:21:56,041
[LUNAR]
Sun Seto, before long,

565
00:21:56,125 --> 00:21:58,666
no one's going
to love you anymore.

566
00:22:04,833 --> 00:22:09,791
♪

567
00:23:34,541 --> 00:23:35,625
[NAGASUMI]
The plot is thickening!

568
00:23:35,708 --> 00:23:37,208
Our school is
in serious danger of

569
00:23:37,291 --> 00:23:38,916
being ripped apart
by senseless violence!

570
00:23:39,000 --> 00:23:40,666
Warring factions
have taken over.

571
00:23:40,750 --> 00:23:42,375
This is bad!
What should I do?

572
00:23:42,458 --> 00:23:43,958
Lunar, why can't you go
back to being the sweet,

573
00:23:44,041 --> 00:23:45,541
modest, talented girl you were?

574
00:23:45,625 --> 00:23:48,958
Oh, that was never really you?
Damn celebrities.

